{"tid":2379000,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓媒爭住報丨大陸網紅撞樣IU 網民：可以頒獎","createTime":"2021-01-25T02:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T12:52:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f53609586c08985e74f8c0b52361db2828a00993","tid":2379000,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k2CCOS_wQZoOU6UhpwRag1iLwaY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R5XPRIAS3JBPFMQTZWAY2CRJLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk2CCOS_wQZoOU6UhpwRag1iLwaY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR5XPRIAS3JBPFMQTZWAY2CRJLI.jpg&h=f2d0171c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸IU樣貌被指有99%撞樣正牌IU（小圖）。<br />\n<br />\n韓國27歲「國民妹妹」IU樣子甜美，出道以來一直深得男性fans的支持，是不少少男心目中的女神。而近日有一名大陸網民因樣貌同IU的樣子有99%相似，所以連韓媒都爭住報道。<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議<br />\n根據韓媒報道，最近在網上一名長得像IU的大陸人成為話題，據了解該名大陸網紅在Tik Tok不時上載有關談論美容的短片，有網民就發現她的樣貌與IU有99%相似，令一眾網民都紛紛留言：「怎麼會長得這麼像」、「可以頒發相似IU的獎項嗎？」等，引起網民熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Uf6E-IP-TkgyVRcTbtxdNzdCedc=/802x570/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S3NCDKTLPJEHLNPLS2OTVMUDYY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUf6E-IP-TkgyVRcTbtxdNzdCedc%3D%2F802x570%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS3NCDKTLPJEHLNPLS2OTVMUDYY.png&h=2487e16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PhMCEwOccD9-8jWZ0FGKw8QLgQI=/802x1414/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P4TJVQF2K5DHBLL5EDRTTY7FJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPhMCEwOccD9-8jWZ0FGKw8QLgQI%3D%2F802x1414%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP4TJVQF2K5DHBLL5EDRTTY7FJM.jpg&h=2e82fdbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/utlQOaqogKLD-StWELMyHghxYkw=/802x1110/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HNMTIKLOTBHIDONVHXUVOJF5IA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FutlQOaqogKLD-StWELMyHghxYkw%3D%2F802x1110%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHNMTIKLOTBHIDONVHXUVOJF5IA.png&h=2dbf90e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6G0ouY4fFnWkA7pepG7RE9inKfU=/802x1015/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PQZNX2CAWZAOTCOUFMD7ZDA7NM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6G0ouY4fFnWkA7pepG7RE9inKfU%3D%2F802x1015%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPQZNX2CAWZAOTCOUFMD7ZDA7NM.jpg&h=c6985160&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3399f61a3e51883d095a4a0e9b7b3ffd28aa7eb0","tid":2379000,"uid":188322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"冇波"},{"pid":"c208c5530aa746288bd2facb88e15d987ec316b3","tid":2379000,"uid":196751,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇過條片就會發現爭好遠<br />\n樣似,氣質都抄唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fcb7cb230d0e75f1f867fe976823c373f199ae","tid":2379000,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"痴痴地..."},{"pid":"bb5667adfc28f825e5a70a6a5398909d9f348c72","tid":2379000,"uid":16659,"like":10,"di